@startuml
title Gambar 5.19 Sequence Diagram Pengelolaan Sewa Aset

actor BPKAD
participant "Penyewaan Page" as PenyewaanPage
participant "Sewa API" as SewaAPI
participant "Auth Middleware" as AuthMiddleware
database "SewaAset Model" as SewaModel

BPKAD -> PenyewaanPage: Mengisi data penyewaan
PenyewaanPage -> SewaAPI: POST/PUT /api/sewa
SewaAPI -> AuthMiddleware: Validasi token dan permission
AuthMiddleware --> SewaAPI: Akses valid
SewaAPI -> SewaModel: Menyimpan data sewa
SewaModel --> SewaAPI: Data sewa tersimpan
SewaAPI --> PenyewaanPage: Respons sukses
PenyewaanPage --> BPKAD: Menampilkan konfirmasi

@enduml
